The paper discusses the integration of IoT technology with human augmentation, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also covers connectivity demands and security aspects, which are relevant to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses design principles and emerging applications, which could be categorized under cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
